{"tid":661912,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜香港再次成為殖民地","createTime":"2018-05-12T03:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T04:28:36.000Z","uid":48240,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"adb0caeab3e4dd66ef50e236d1c134ccd9902306","tid":661912,"uid":48240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"從97後開始計<br />\n每日150個單程証<br />\n一年就接近 5萬5千個中國人落嚟<br />\n二十年以嚟就有 110 萬個中國人落咗嚟我港<br />\n再計返佢地平均都會生一個<br />\n單純數字上推測 回歸到依家總共已經有 220萬 隻腥港人<br />\n<br />\n睇返2017年底數據<br />\n香港總人口大約係 740萬<br />\n呢220萬腥香港人佔咗香港總人口既大約 30%<br />\n<br />\n再純粹猜測：<br />\n佢地入住公屋比率保守高達 70%<br />\n拎老綜比率高達 50%<br />\n<br />\n由此可見<br />\n本土香港人好快唔再係主流聲音<br />\n大家搵既錢將繼續供養腥港人<br />\n而住屋樓價將不繼上升<br />\n香港人買得起樓既為數會愈嚟愈少<br />\n生下一代既人因此會一直下降<br />\n反之腥港人會係咁生<br />\n因為政府會幫手養<br />\n所以唔洗到 2047 香港人將正式成為香港本土既少數民族<br />\n<br />\n各位好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e93b1cfb379ba6609b88daac7e908cf086de521","tid":661912,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:35:37.000Z","msg":"仲衰撚過英治時期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82725bc9850b94021a4d3d5d80df26a229b32ca","tid":661912,"uid":48240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e93b1cfb379ba6609b88daac7e908cf086de521","tid":661912,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:35:37.000Z","msg":"仲衰撚過英治時期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"不久將來，好快廣東話會絕跡於香港"},{"pid":"b6ad954bd65fc75d41ed32704416dd10549f114c","tid":661912,"uid":48240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"廣東話好快連方言都算唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以淋病月痾都唔算有講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f11b17efec8ed877424afdc2681f6cdc20f1dba","tid":661912,"uid":20072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"到我地4~50 歲就會變成淨係識講老土鄉下廣東話既廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4340e621f07c122562dbac1e46a993024861b46e","tid":661912,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>成為精英，逃離香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ee9d59e46a3f01d4f0708551780dbd8b58c5a294","tid":661912,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:28:36.000Z","msg":"「推普中」從不學術：只是一個「後殖民」的政治操作<br />\n<br />\n因為，殖民統治者不跟本地學者談學術問題，因為他著眼之處從來不是真理的對錯糾纏，只要他的聲音比其他人都更大，反覆話語論述鋪天蓋地足以掩飾一切，大抵三人成虎，劣幣驅逐良幣，達成最後的政治結果，才是最重要的事。<br />\n<br />\n不要再講學術了，再這樣糾纏下去沒有什麼效用，這只是一個政治的操作，必須政治地觀看。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%B0%BC%E6%80%9D%E5%8C%96/%E6%8E%A8%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%AD-%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93-%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C-87defc761c66\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%258C%2596%2F%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25AE%2596%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%2593%258D%25E4%25BD%259C-87defc761c66&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c11e0cf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%B0%BC%E6%80%9D%E5%8C%96/%E6%8E%A8%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%AD-%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93-%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C-87defc761c66</a>"}]}